data.description: GORGEOUS Perry Home located on a quiet, secluded cul-de-sac in sought-after Oak Run.  The grand entryway features a vaulted ceiling leading to a spacious Family Room with a stone gas fireplace and a wall of windows to view the full-length, 38x17 covered backyard patio w/firepit.  Green Belt allows privacy to enjoy entertaining guests, playing outdoor games or relaxing among the Gorgeous Oak Trees and Beautiful Landscaping.  Real Hardwood Floors throughout main floor, Beautiful Kitchen features an Island, granite countertops, a double oven, Breakfast Room or enjoy conversation at the Breakfast Bar.  Dining Room and Private Study sit in front of the home.  Upstairs offers an open and large Game/Media Room.  This Home boasts over 3500 sq ft (per old appraisal) detached and insulated garage, generous size private bedrooms and bathrooms, walk-in closets and surround sound.  A private view of a breathtaking backyard that expands onto the wildlife and nature of an undisturbed Green Belt.
